title: Ong Chin Wen
data: Ong Chin Wen is a Malaysian politician who served as Member of Penang State Legislative Assembly (MLA) for Bukit Tengah seat from March 2008 to May 2018. He is a member of Sabah Heritage Party (WARISAN) and was a member of People's Justice Party (PKR), a component party of Pakatan Harapan (PH).[1]
